<p><a name="Related_websites" id="Related_websites"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Handwriting_recognition&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Related websites">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Related websites</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://users.erols.com/rwservices/pens/penhist.html" class="external text" title="http://users.erols.com/rwservices/pens/penhist.html" rel="nofollow">The Unknown History of Handwriting Recognition</a> contains a history of handwriting recognition and related topics from approximately 1917 to 1992.</li>
<li><a href="http://rwservices.no-ip.info:81/biblio.html" class="external text" title="http://rwservices.no-ip.info:81/biblio.html" rel="nofollow">Annotated bibliography of references to handwriting recognition and pen computing</a></li>
<li><a href="http://risujin.org/cellwriter" class="external text" title="http://risujin.org/cellwriter" rel="nofollow">Cellwriter</a> an open-source grid-entry natural handwriting input panel. The site also features a thesis with some information about the algorithms</li>
<li><a href="http://hal.inria.fr/IWFHR10/en" class="external text" title="http://hal.inria.fr/IWFHR10/en" rel="nofollow">International Workshop for Frontiers in Handwriting Recognition</a> Homepage of the 2006 workshop. Upgraded to a conference starting 2008.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.icdar2007.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.icdar2007.org/" rel="nofollow">International Conference for Document Analysis and Recognition</a> Homepage of the 2007 conference.</li>
<li><a href="http://lipitk.sourceforge.net" class="external text" title="http://lipitk.sourceforge.net" rel="nofollow">Lipi Toolkit</a> An Open Source toolkit for Online Handwriting Recognition</li>
<li>Neocognitron was initially suggested by Kunihiko Fukushima, as a neural model for pattern recognition, it has been used for handwritten character recognition too. Neocognitron <b>application</b> (C#) and <b>video</b> about the simulator are available: <a href="http://neocognitron.euweb.cz/index.html" class="external text" title="http://neocognitron.euweb.cz/index.html" rel="nofollow">here</a></li>
<li>Beholder, a Neocognitron demo project - <a href="http://www.nin.knaw.nl/~korjouko/projects/beholder2/index.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.nin.knaw.nl/~korjouko/projects/beholder2/index.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.nin.knaw.nl/~korjouko/projects/beholder2/index.htm</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Vendors_and_links_to_commercial_sites" id="Vendors_and_links_to_commercial_sites"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Handwriting_recognition&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Vendors and links to commercial sites">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Vendors and links to commercial sites</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.a2ia.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.a2ia.com/" rel="nofollow">A2iA - Artificial Intelligence and Image Analysis</a> A2iA a software company that operates one of the world’s largest research centers focusing on ways to extract information from everyday paper documents that contain handwritten information.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ariolis.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.ariolis.com/" rel="nofollow">Ariolis Form Processing Solutions</a> ArioForm - Form Processing software and solutions with advanced handwriting recognition technology &amp; features.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ritescript.com/Products/ritePen.aspx" class="external text" title="http://www.ritescript.com/Products/ritePen.aspx" rel="nofollow">ritePen page</a> EverNote Corporation's website.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.visionobjects.com/handwriting-recognition/" class="external text" title="http://www.visionobjects.com/handwriting-recognition/" rel="nofollow">online handwriting recognition and potential applications</a> Vision Objects' website.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.phatware.com/penoffice/" class="external text" title="http://www.phatware.com/penoffice/" rel="nofollow">Pen-based collaboration and handwriting recognition software for Windows</a> PhatWare Corporation website.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.phatware.com/developer/" class="external text" title="http://www.phatware.com/developer/" rel="nofollow">CalliGrapher handwriting recognition technology and SDK</a> PhatWare Corporation website.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.neoptec.com/en/products/data-scan/presentation.php" class="external text" title="http://www.neoptec.com/en/products/data-scan/presentation.php" rel="nofollow">Data-Scan form-processing software</a> The page on Neoptec's website devoted to software for automatically capturing hand-printed data from documents.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.wacom.com/index2.cfm/" class="external text" title="http://www.wacom.com/index2.cfm/" rel="nofollow">Bamboo Tablet</a> Wacom's Bamboo and Bamboo Fun are two reasonably priced pen tablets.</li>
</ul>


